altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크 - 버전 27
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 27
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v27 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Mario Superstar Baseball, and Chicken Little. The disc also features videos of the following: Battalion Wars, The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess, Mario Superstar Baseball, Medal of Honor: European Assault, The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, Charlie and the Chocolate Factory, Chicken Little, Madden NFL 06, Fantastic 4, WWE Day of Reckoning 2, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
